    "description": {
      "value": "<p><strong>Category:</strong> Clan<br /><strong>Prerequisite:</strong> Claymore Clan<br />You have refined both your blade and technique as far as pure talent can. You gain the following benefits:</p><ul><li>Increase your Strength, or Dexterity score by 1, to a maximum of 20.</li><li>Your <strong>Claymore</strong> has its quality increased by 1 rank and this quality rank increases when you would reach the Enhancement Seal Minimum Level Requirement the quality is automatically increased to that quality.</li><li><p>Once per turn when you hit a creature with your Claymore you may force them to make a Strength saving throw to be knocked back 30 feet or be knocked prone.</p><pre><code></code></pre></li></ul>",
